 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:blue;font-size:10pt\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:#a31515;font-size:10pt\">Grid.RowDefinitions</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:blue;font-size:10pt\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:blue;font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:#a31515;font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:blue;font-size:10pt\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:#a31515;font-size:10pt\">TextBlock</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:red;font-size:10pt\"> Text</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:blue;font-size:10pt\">=&quot;Click here to add a new item.&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:red;font-size:10pt\"> Grid.Column</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:blue;font-size:10pt\">=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:#a31515;font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:#a31515;font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';color:#a31515;font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><s